Description: A language with a focus on simplicity, safety and correctness
 Fuzion is a modern programming language that emphasizes simplicity,
 safety, and correctness. It features algebraic effects, design by
 contract, and a unified feature system that eliminates the distinction
 between classes, methods, and interfaces.
 .
 This package contains the Fuzion compiler, runtime library, and
 language server.
